</section>

<!--Privacy section-->
<section>

	<div class="text-center" style="margin-top:2%;margin-bottom:2%;">
		<h4 class="display-4"><strong>Privacy</strong></h4>

		<br />

		<p class="display-4">Flute cares about your privacy when dealing with your data.</p>

		<br />

		<h4>Storage of data</h4>
		<br />

		<p>We take security very seriously, we take many precautions when dealing with your training information. These include:</p>

		<p>Transmitting your training data using encrypted channels.</p>
		<p>Encrypting training data at rest.</p>
		<p>Scrubbing training files once trained: - once we train your model, we save the model file for re-use in encrypted storage, then, we permanently delete every instance of your training data.</p>

		<p style="font-weight:bold;">
			NOTE: 
			We encourage your to review your training data carefully before uploading it, ask yourself 'Are Jane's first name, last name and D.O.B really helpful features to train this model?'
		</p>
	</div>
	<br />
</section>